 peace and blessings be upon him, begin his prayer when he awakened at night?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWhen the Prophet awakened at night, he would exalt\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34861,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/27\/ruku-between-sajdatayn\/","url_meta":{"origin":42209,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Supplication after bowing, between prostrations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: He prayed one night with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he heard him when he announced the opening exaltation, \u201cAllah is the greatest, O possessor of power, dominion, grandeur, and might.\u201d The Prophet said in his bowing, \u201cGlory be to Allah the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33170,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/11\/what-imam-says-in-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":42209,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: What the Imam and followers say in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah heard those who praise him,\u201d he would say, \u201cO Allah, our Lord, for you is praise.\u201d When the Prophet bowed and raised his head, he would declare the greatness of Allah. When he stood from the\u